    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC is a re-release of RFC 1098, with a changed "Status of this Memo" section plus a few minor typographical corrections.  This memo defines a simple protocol by which management information for a network element may be inspected or altered by logically remote users. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
